high_descs: Turn right, cross the kitchen, and turn right again after the island, so you end facing the dishwasher next to the sink.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter above the dishwasher.
Carry the lettuce to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the lettuce on the top shelf, close the door, and then remove the lettuce after a couple seconds.
Turn left and carry the lettuce back to the kitchen sink.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled lettuce on the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink, turn right, move to the lettuce on the counter on the left, turn left to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right, bring the lettuce to the fridge, turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Take the chilled lettuce to the counter, past the sink on the left.
Put the lettuce on the counter, left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Walk right and right again and face the lettuce on the left.
Grab the lettuce off of the counter.
Walk forward and face the fridge on the left.
Chill the lettuce for 4 seconds on the top shelf.
Walk left and face the sink on the right.
Place the lettuce to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled lettuce to the left of the sink.
